{
  "S04n486:0": "sarvadharmasvabhāvasamatāvipañcita-",
  "S04n486:1": "samādhirājasūtram | 1",
  "S04n486:3": "nidānaparivartaḥ |",
  "S04n486:4": "evaṃ mayā śrutam |",
  "S04n486:5": "ekasmin samaye bhagavān rājagṛhe viharati sma gṛdhrakūṭe parvate mahatā",
  "S04n486:6": "bhikṣusaṃghena sārdhaṃ paripūrṇena bhikṣuniyutaśatasahasreṇa aśītyā ca bodhisattvaniyutaiḥ sārdham |",
  "S04n486:7": "sarvairakajātipratibaddhairabhijñābhijñātairdaśadiglokadhātusaṃnipatitairdhāraṇīsūtrāntagatiṃ gataiḥ sarvasattvadharmadānasaṃtoṣakairmahābhijñājñānodāhārakuśalaiḥ sarvapāramitāparamapāramitāprāptaiḥ sarvabodhisattvasamādhisamāpattivyavasthānajñānakuśalaiḥ sarvabuddhastutastobhitapraśastaiḥ sarvabuddhakṣetravyākramaṇakuśalaiḥ sarvamārasaṃtrāsanajñānakuśalaiḥ sarvadharmayathāvajjñānakuśalaiḥ sarvasattvendriyaparāparajñānakuśalaiḥ buddhasarvakarmapūjāsamādānaprajñānakuśalaiḥ sarvalokadharmānupaliptaiḥ kāyavākcittasamalaṃkṛtaiḥ mahāmaitrīmahākaruṇāsaṃnāhasaṃnaddhaiḥ mahāvīryāsaṃkhyeyakalpāparikṣīṇamānasaiḥ mahāsiṃhanādanādibhiḥ sarvaparapravādānabhibhūtaiḥ avaivartikamudrāmudritaiḥ sarvabuddhadharmābhiṣekaprāptaiḥ |",
  "S04n486:8": "tadyathā-meruṇā ca nāma bodhisattvena mahāsattvena |",
  "S04n486:9": "sumeruṇā ca |",
