  "S04n486:34": "lakṣaṇasamalaṃkṛtena ca |",
  "S04n486:35": "svaravyūhena ca |",
  "S04n486:36": "svaraviśuddhiprabheṇa ca |",
  "S04n486:37": "ratnakūṭena ca |",
  "S04n486:38": "ratnacūḍena ca |",
  "S04n486:39": "daśaśataraśmikṛtārciṣā jyoti rasena ca |",
  "S04n486:40": "candrabhānunā ca |",
  "S04n486:41": "sahacittotpādadharmacakrapravartinā ca |",
  "S04n486:42": "śubhakanakaviśuddhiprabheṇa ca |",
  "S04n486:43": "satatamabhayaṃdadānena ca nāma bodhisattvena mahāsattvena |",
  "S04n486:44": "ajitabodhisattvapūrvaṃgamaiśca sarvairbhadrakalpikairbodhisattvairmahāsattvaiḥ |",
  "S04n486:45": "mañjuśrīpūrvaṃgamaiśca ṣaṣṭibhiranupamacittaiḥ |",
  "S04n486:46": "bhadrapālapūrvaṃgamaiśca ṣoḍaśabhiḥ satpuruṣaiḥ |",
  "S04n486:47": "caturmahārājapūrvaṃgamaiśca cāturmahārājakāyikairdevaputraiḥ |",
  "S04n486:48": "peyālam |",
  "S04n486:49": "yāvad brahmapūrvaṃgamaiśca brahmakāyikairdevaputraistadanyaiśca maheśākhyamaheśākhyairudārodārairdevanāgayakṣagandharvāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragamanuṣyāmanuṣyai rbhagavān satkṛto gurukṛto mānitaḥ pūjito'rcito'pacāyitaścatasṛṇāmapi parṣadāṃ sadevalokasya lokasya vandanīyaḥ pūjanīyo namaskaraṇīyaḥ |",
  "S04n486:50": "tatra khalu bhagavānanekaśatasahasrayā parṣadā parivṛtaḥ puraskṛto dharmaṃ deśayati sma ādau kalyāṇaṃ madhye kalyāṇaṃ paryavasāne kalyāṇam |",
  "S04n486:51": "svarthaṃ suvyañjanaṃ kevalaṃ paripūrṇaṃ pariśuddhaṃ paryavadātaṃ brahmacaryaṃ saṃprakāśayati sma ||",
  "S04n486:52": "tena khalu punaḥ samayena tasminneva parṣatsaṃnipāte candraprabho nāma kumārabhūtaḥ saṃnipatito'bhūt saṃniṣaṇṇaḥ pūrvajinakṛtādhikāro'varopitakuśalamūlo jātismaro labdhapratibhāno mahāyānasaṃprasthito mahākaruṇābhiyuktaḥ |",
  "S04n486:53": "atha khalu candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūta utthāyāsanādekāṃsamuttarāsaṅgaṃ prāvṛtya dakṣiṇaṃ jānumaṇḍalaṃ pṛthivyāṃ pratiṣṭhāpya yena bhagavāṃstenāñjaliṃ praṇamya bhagavantametadavocat-pṛccheyamahaṃ bhagavantaṃ tathāgatamarhantaṃ samyaksaṃbuddhaṃ kaṃcideva pradeśam,",
  "S04n486:54": "sacenme bhagavānavakāśaṃ kuryāt pṛṣṭapraśnavyākaraṇāya |",
  "S04n486:55": "evamukte bhagavān candraprabhaṃ kumārabhūtamāmantrayate sma-pṛccha tvaṃ kumārabhūta tathāgatamarhantaṃ samyaksaṃbuddhaṃ yad yadeva kāṅkṣasi |",
  "S04n486:56": "ahaṃ tasya tasyaiva praśnasya pṛṣṭasya vyākaraṇena cittamārādhayiṣyāmi |",
  "S04n486:57": "sarvajño'smi samyaksaṃbuddhaḥ kumāra sarvadarśī sarvadharmabalavaiśāradyavṛṣabhatāmanuprāpto'nāvaraṇavimokṣajñānasamanvāgataḥ |",
  "S04n486:58": "nāsti kumāra tathāgatasya sarvadharmeṣvajñātaṃ vā adṛṣṭaṃ vā aśrutaṃ vā aviditaṃ vā asākṣātkṛtaṃ vā anabhisaṃbuddhaṃ vā anantāparyanteṣu lokadhātuṣu |",
  "S04n486:59": "nityakṛtaste kumāra avakāśo bhavatu tathāgataṃ praśnaparipṛcchanāya |",
  "S04n486:60": "ahaṃ te tasya tasyaiva praśnasya pṛṣṭasya vyākaraṇena cittamārādhayiṣyāmi ||",
  "S04n486:61": "atha khalu candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūtastuṣṭa udagra āttamanāḥ pramuditaḥ prītisaumanasyajātastasyāṃ velāyāṃ bhagavantaṃ gāthābhiradhyabhāṣata-",
  "S04n486:62": "kathaṃ carantaḥ saṃbuddha lokanātha prabhaṃkara |",
  "S04n486:63": "labhate'cintiyaṃ jñānaṃ vyākuruṣva hitaṃkara || 1 ||",
  "S04n486:64": "kathaṃ carantu narendra satyavādi",
  "S04n486:65": "naravṛṣabha naradevapūjanīya |",
  "S04n486:66": "atuliyu varu labdhamagrayāṇaṃ",
  "S04n486:67": "giravara pṛṣṭa viyākuruṣva nātha || 2 ||",
  "S04n486:68": "adhyāśayena pṛcchāmi śāṭhyaṃ mama na vidyate |",
  "S04n486:69": "sākṣī na kaścidanyo me anyatra puruṣottamāt || 3 ||",
  "S04n486:70": "vipula praṇidhi mahyamasti chanda-",
  "S04n486:71": "ścariya prajānasi mahya śākyasiṃha |",
  "S04n486:72": "na ca ahaṃ vacanavittako bhaviṣye",
  "S04n486:73": "laghu pratipatti bhaṇāhi me narendra || 4 ||",
  "S04n486:74": "katarāhārakā dharmā buddhayāne bahuṃkarāḥ |",
  "S04n486:75": "vyākuruṣva mahāvīra sarvadharmāṇa pāraga || 5 ||",
  "S04n486:76": "upakare dharma mama brūhi nātha",
  "S04n486:77": "yatha naru niṣevatu bhoti tīkṣṇaprajñaḥ |",
  "S04n486:78": "apagatabhayabhairavo atrasto",
  "S04n486:79": "na ca parityāgu karoti śīlaskandhāt |",
  "S04n486:80": "vyapagatamadarāgadoṣamoha-",
  "S04n486:81": "ścarati ca cārika sarvaśāntadoṣaḥ || 6 ||",
  "S04n486:82": "kathaṃ na tyajate śīlaṃ kathaṃ dhyānaṃ na riñcati |",
  "S04n486:83": "kathaṃ niṣevate'raṇyaṃ kathaṃ prajñā pravartate || 7 ||",
  "S04n486:84": "kathaṃ daśabalaśāsane udāre",
  "S04n486:85": "abhirati vindati śīla rakṣamāṇaḥ |",
  "S04n486:86": "kathaṃ bhavati acchidru śīlaskandhaḥ",
  "S04n486:87": "kathaṃ ca tuleti svabhāvu saṃskṛtasya || 8 ||",
  "S04n486:88": "kathaṃ kāyena vācā pariśuddho bhoti paṇḍitaḥ |",
  "S04n486:89": "asaṃkliṣṭena cittena buddhajñānaṃ niṣevate || 9 ||",
  "S04n486:90": "kathaṃ bhavati viśuddhakāyakarmā",
  "S04n486:91": "kathaṃ ca vivarjita bhonti vācadoṣāḥ |",
  "S04n486:92": "kathaṃ bhavati asaṃkliṣṭacittaḥ",
  "S04n486:93": "puruṣavara mama pṛṣṭa vyākuruṣva || 10 ||",
  "S04n486:94": "atha khalu bhagavāṃścandraprabhaṃ kumārabhūtametadavocat-ekadharmeṇa kumāra samanvāgato bodhisattvo mahāsattva etān guṇān pratilabhate,",
  "S04n486:95": "kṣipraṃ cānuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisaṃbudhyate |",
  "S04n486:96": "katamenaikadharmeṇa ?",
  "S04n486:97": "iha kumāra bodhisattvo mahāsattvaḥ sarvasattveṣu samacitto bhavati hitacitto'pratihatacitto'viṣamacittaḥ |",
  "S04n486:98": "anena kumāra ekadharmeṇa samanvāgato bodhisattvo mahāsattva etān guṇān pratilabhate kṣipraṃ cānuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhimabhisaṃbudhyate ||",
  "S04n486:99": "atha khalu bhagavāṃstasyāṃ velāyāṃ candraprabhaṃ kumārabhūtaṃ gāthābhiradhyabhāṣata-",
  "S04n486:100": "ekadharmaṃ samādāya bodhisattvo ya vartate |",
  "S04n486:101": "etān guṇān sa labhate kṣipraṃ bodhiṃ ca budhyate || 11 ||",
  "S04n486:102": "na ca kaści pratihanyate'sya cittam",
  "S04n486:103": "apratihatacittu yo bhoti bodhisattvaḥ |",
  "S04n486:104": "na ca khilu janayati na pradoṣaṃ",
  "S04n486:105": "labhati yathā parikīrtitān viśeṣān || 12 ||",
  "S04n486:106": "samaṃ cittaṃ niṣevitvā vipāko darśitaḥ samaḥ |",
  "S04n486:107": "samāḥ pādatalā bhonti samaścācāragocaraḥ || 13 ||",
  "S04n486:108": "samamaviṣamacittu bhāvayitvā",
  "S04n486:109": "apagatadoṣakhilaḥ prahīṇakāṅkṣaḥ |",
  "S04n486:110": "caraṇavaratalāḥ samāsya bhonti",
  "S04n486:111": "paramaprabhāsvara śuddhadarśanīyaḥ || 14 ||",
  "S04n486:112": "daśadiśita viroci bodhisattvaḥ",
  "S04n486:113": "sphurati śirīya prabhāya buddhakṣetram |",
  "S04n486:114": "yada bhavati sa labdhu śāntabhūmi",
  "S04n486:115": "tada bahusattva sthapeti buddhajñāne || 15 ||",
  "S04n486:116": "tatra kumāra sarvasattveṣu samacitto bodhisattvo mahāsattvo hitacitto'pratihatacitto'viṣamacittaṃ imaṃ sarvadharmasvabhāvasamatāvipañcitaṃ nāma samādhiṃ pratilabhate |",
  "S04n486:117": "katamaśca sa kumāra sarvadharmasvabhāvasamatāvipañcitaṃ nāma samādhiḥ pratilabhate |",
  "S04n486:118": "katamaśca sa kumāra sarvadharmasvabhāvasamatāvipañcito nāma samādhiḥ ?",
